I hope this email finds you well. I am reaching out to formally bring to
your attention a persistent sewage issue at Shady Oaks Park MHP LLC,
specifically concerning Lot 21, located directly across from my residence (=
Lot
17).

=F0=9F=93=8C ISSUE SUMMARY:

   - The area around Lot 21 has been continuously emitting sewage, creating
   both a health concern and an environmental hazard.
   - This issue was previously reported to Kim in March 2024, at which time
   we were informed that the matter had been resolved.
   - However, as of March 7, 2025, the issue appears to be ongoing.

=F0=9F=93=8C REQUEST FOR RESOLUTION:
I understand that unforeseen maintenance issues can arise, and I appreciate
the efforts that management has made in the past to address concerns. That
said, given the potential health risks and impact on the community, I
kindly request that this matter be revisited and properly resolved.

=F0=9F=93=8C NEXT STEPS:
I would appreciate a written response within 48 hours (by March 9,
2025) regarding
the planned course of action. If a work order has already been issued or a
repair is scheduled, please let me know so that I can update my records
accordingly.

I value open communication and trust that Shady Oaks will take appropriate
action to resolve this matter. Please let me know if there is anything I
can do to assist in addressing this issue.

Thank you for your time and prompt attention to this matter.

Sincerely,
Andrew Pigors
Lot 17

